Class DatabaseEntry

java.lang.Object
  model.classes.DatabaseEntry
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConditionEntry, ConditionTag, ConditionUser
public abstract class DatabaseEntry
extends java.lang.Object

This abstract class represents rows in the application database. This abstraction allows different types of DatabaseEntry objects to be displayed in a ListView or Spinner.
